<br />
Thanks for this article, I'm sure I'll end up experimenting more with it in the future.</div>
					<hr size="1" noshade />
				
					<hr size="1" noshade />
					<div class="commentheading">On August 11, 2005 at 06:28 AM, Hui May (guest) said...</div>
