					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Re: making cupcake size with this recipe</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody"><div class='commentquote'>ccgabbie wrote:<div class='commentquotebody'>hi, I would like to make this recipe, but how would I cook it to use in cupcake sizes?? I would like to make individual cakes. I also do not have a springform, only round cake pans. <br />
