					<div class="commentheading">On July 15, 2009 at 11:22 PM, Michael Chu said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Re: Do you have to coat the sides of the pan with butter?</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody"><div class='commentquote'>cheesycake wrote:<div class='commentquotebody'>So when you put the batter in, do you have to coat the sides of the pan with butter/cooking spray so it wont stick when you take it out, or will it just come out by itself?</div></div><br />
