					<div class="commentbody">So the cake looks &amp; smells fantastic but I've made a million &amp; one cheesecakes so I had to make it differently to make it my own. First of all use a nut such as pecans for the crust, or choclate cookies like oreos crushed if making it a peanut butter cream cheese cake, always better. Also be playful with your recipes &amp; substitute the whip cream with twice as much white chocolate mousse &amp; layer in your favorite fruits then top with more fruit after it has chilled or on individual slices if you're like me &amp; want to experience e something different with each serving. <br />
